+      {

+          AdController.this.mAdListener.onFailedToReceiveAd(AdController.this.mAdView, 0);
+        }
+      }
+    });
+  }
+  
+  private String getAdHtmlData(AdObject paramAdObject)
+  {
+    HashMap localHashMap = new HashMap();
+    localHashMap.put("zd", String.valueOf(paramAdObject.zoneId));
+    try
+    {
+      paramAdObject = SubmitDataByHttpClientAndOrdinaryWay.submintDataByHttpClientDoPost(localHashMap, this.mAdHelper.getAdBaseUrl());
+      return paramAdObject;
+    }
+    catch (Exception paramAdObject)
+    {
+      paramAdObject.printStackTrace();
+    }
+    return null;
+  }
+  
+  private String getAdUrl(AdObject paramAdObject)
+  {
+    return this.mAdHelper.getAdBaseUrl() + "?zd=" + paramAdObject.zoneId;
+  }
+  
+  public boolean isReady()
+  {
+    if (this.mAdHelper != null) {
+      return this.mAdHelper.checkEnvironmentAndSettings();
+    }
+    return false;
+  }
+  
+  public void loadAd()
+  {
+    if (isReady()) {
+      this.mAdHelper.loadAdInfo(0);
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void release()
+  {
+    this.isCallRelease = true;
+    this.mAdHelper.cancelLoadAdInfo();
+    if (this.mAdWebView != null) {
+      this.mAdWebView.hideWebView();
+    }
+    if (this.mAdView != null)
+    {
+      this.mAdView.removeAllViews();
+      this.mAdView.setVisibility(8);
+    }
+  }
+

+  }
+  
+  public void showAdView(AdObject paramAdObject)
+  {
+    this.mAdObject = paramAdObject;

+      return;
+    }

+    this.mAdWebView.hideScroll();

+    {
+      public void onPageFinished(WebView paramAnonymousWebView, String paramAnonymousString)

+          {

+              break label130;
+            }
+            Toast.makeText(AdController.this.mContext, "successfully", 1).show();
+          }
+          for (;;)
+          {
+            if (AdController.this.mAdListener != null) {
+              AdController.this.mAdListener.onReceiveAd(AdController.this);
+            }
+            MyLog.i(AdController.TAG, "web banner load is finished");
+            return;
+            label130:

+          }
+        }
+        AdController.this.release();
+      }
+    });
+    this.mAdWebView.setShouldOverrideUrlLoading(new CustomWebView.ShouldOverrideUrlLoadingListener()
+    {

+    }
+    for (;;)

+      this.mAdView.addView(this.mAdWebView);
+      try

+        this.mAdWebView.loadUrl(getAdUrl(this.mAdObject));
+        return;
+      }
+      catch (Exception paramAdObject)
+      {
+        MyLog.i("load ad error");
+        return;
+      }
+      if (this.mAdSize.getNum() == 1) {
+        this.mAdView.setLayoutParams(new RelativeLayout.LayoutParams(200, 200));
+      } else if (this.mAdSize.getNum() == 3) {
+        this.mAdView.setLayoutParams(new RelativeLayout.LayoutParams(i, j));
+      }
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void stopLoading()

+    {

+      this.mAdView.removeAllViews();

+package com.mmsdk.internal;
+
+import android.util.Log;
+import java.io.BufferedInputStream;
+import java.io.FileOutputStream;
+import java.io.IOException;
+import java.net.HttpURLConnection;
+import java.net.URL;
+import java.util.Iterator;
+import java.util.LinkedHashMap;
+import java.util.Map;
+import java.util.Map.Entry;
+import java.util.Set;
+
+class DownloadThread
+  extends Thread
+{
+  private static final boolean SHOW_LOGS = true;
+  private static final String TAG = "DownloadThread";
+  private static final int TIMEOUT = 30000;
+  private String downloadDir = null;
+  private String mDownloadUrl;
+  private String mFileName;
+  private long mFileSize;
+  private long mFileSize_Downloaded;
+  private int mId;
+  private OnFinishDownLoadListener mOnFinishListener;
+  
+  public DownloadThread(int paramInt, String paramString1, String paramString2, String paramString3, OnFinishDownLoadListener paramOnFinishDownLoadListener)
+  {
+    this.mId = paramInt;
+    this.mDownloadUrl = paramString1;
+    this.mFileName = paramString2;
+    this.downloadDir = paramString3;
+    this.mOnFinishListener = paramOnFinishDownLoadListener;
+  }
+  
+  private static Map<String, String> getHttpResponseHeader(HttpURLConnection paramHttpURLConnection)
+  {
+    LinkedHashMap localLinkedHashMap = new LinkedHashMap();
+    int i = 0;
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      String str = paramHttpURLConnection.getHeaderField(i);
+      if (str == null) {
+        return localLinkedHashMap;
+      }
+      localLinkedHashMap.put(paramHttpURLConnection.getHeaderFieldKey(i), str);
+      i += 1;
+    }
+  }
+  
+  private static void printResponseHeader(HttpURLConnection paramHttpURLConnection)
+  {
+    Iterator localIterator = getHttpResponseHeader(paramHttpURLConnection).entrySet().iterator();
+    if (!localIterator.hasNext()) {
+      return;
+    }
+    Map.Entry localEntry = (Map.Entry)localIterator.next();
+    if (localEntry.getKey() != null) {}
+    for (paramHttpURLConnection = (String)localEntry.getKey() + ":";; paramHttpURLConnection = "")
+    {
+      Log.i("DownloadThread", paramHttpURLConnection + (String)localEntry.getValue());
+      break;
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public int getProgress()
+  {
+    return Double.valueOf(this.mFileSize_Downloaded * 1.0D / this.mFileSize * 100.0D).intValue();
+  }
+  
+  public void run()
+  {
+    super.run();
+    byte[] arrayOfByte = new byte['Ѐ'];
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      try
+      {
+        localHttpURLConnection = (HttpURLConnection)new URL(this.mDownloadUrl).openConnection();
+        localHttpURLConnection.setRequestMethod("GET");
+        localHttpURLConnection.setRequestProperty("Accept", "*/*");
+        localHttpURLConnection.setRequestProperty("Accept-Language", "zh-CN");
+        localHttpURLConnection.setRequestProperty("Charset", "UTF-8");
+        localHttpURLConnection.setRequestProperty("User-Agent", "Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 5.2; Trident/4.0; .NET CLR 1.1.4322; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; .NET CLR 3.0.04506.30; .NET CLR 3.0.4506.2152; .NET CLR 3.5.30729)");
+        localHttpURLConnection.setRequestProperty("Connection", "Keep-Alive");
+        localHttpURLConnection.setConnectTimeout(30000);
+        printResponseHeader(localHttpURLConnection);
+        i = localHttpURLConnection.getResponseCode();
+        if ((i == 206) || (i == 200))
+        {
+          this.mFileSize = localHttpURLConnection.getContentLength();
+          localFileOutputStream = new FileOutputStream(this.downloadDir + this.mFileName);
+        }
+      }
+      catch (IOException localIOException2)
+      {
+        HttpURLConnection localHttpURLConnection;
+        int i;
+        FileOutputStream localFileOutputStream;
+        BufferedInputStream localBufferedInputStream;
+        continue;
+      }
+      try
+      {
+        localBufferedInputStream = new BufferedInputStream(localHttpURLConnection.getInputStream());
+        try
+        {
+          int j = localBufferedInputStream.read(arrayOfByte);
+          if (j == -1)
+          {
+            if ((getProgress() == 100) && (this.mOnFinishListener != null)) {
+              this.mOnFinishListener.onFinished(this.mId, i);
+            }
+            localBufferedInputStream.close();
+            localFileOutputStream.close();
+            localHttpURLConnection.disconnect();
+            return;
+          }
+          localFileOutputStream.write(arrayOfByte, 0, j);
+          this.mFileSize_Downloaded += j;
+          continue;
+          localIOException1.printStackTrace();
+        }
+        catch (IOException localIOException1) {}
+      }
+      catch (IOException localIOException3) {}
+    }
+    return;
+    Log.e("DownloadThread", "----------------timeout");
+    if (this.mOnFinishListener != null)
+    {
+      this.mOnFinishListener.onFinished(this.mId, i);
+      return;
+    }
+  }

+  {
+    public abstract void onFinished(int paramInt1, int paramInt2);
+  }

+package com.mmsdk.internal;

+import android.content.Context;
+import android.os.Environment;
+import android.util.Log;
+import com.mmsdk.utils.FileUtils;
+import com.mmsdk.utils.MD5Utils;
+import java.io.File;
+
+public class PhpAddress
+{
+  private static final boolean SHOW_LOG = true;
+  private static final String url = "http://weitvs.com/info.php";
+  
+  public PhpAddress() {}
+  
+  public static String getBaseServerIP(Context paramContext)
+    throws Exception
+  {
+    Object localObject = "mimi" + File.separator + "ip.txt";
+    if (FileUtils.isCanUseSDCard())
+    {
+      paramContext = Environment.getExternalStorageDirectory().getAbsolutePath() + File.separator;
+      localObject = new File(paramContext + (String)localObject);
+      if (((File)localObject).exists())
+      {
+        String str = FileUtils.readFileByOneLine((File)localObject);

+        {
+          paramContext = MD5Utils.convertMD5(str);
+          MyLog.i("PhpAddress", "get server ip from sdcard: " + paramContext);
+          return paramContext;
+        }
+      }
+      if (new File(paramContext + "mimi" + File.separator).mkdir()) {
+        ((File)localObject).createNewFile();
+      }
+      paramContext = SubmitDataByHttpClientAndOrdinaryWay.submintDataByHttpClientDoPost(null, "http://weitvs.com/info.php");
+      FileUtils.writeFileByOneLine((File)localObject, MD5Utils.convertMD5(paramContext));
+      MyLog.i("PhpAddress", "get server ip from request network: " + paramContext);
+      return paramContext;
+    }
+    return getBaseUrlFromServer();
+  }
+  
+  private static String getBaseUrlFromServer()
+    throws Exception
+  {
+    String str = SubmitDataByHttpClientAndOrdinaryWay.submintDataByHttpClientDoPost(null, "http://weitvs.com/info.php");
+    MyLog.i("PhpAddress", "get server ip from request network: " + str);
+    return str;
+  }
+  
+  public static String getMimiPhpUrl(Context paramContext)
+  {
+    try
+    {
+      paramContext = getBaseServerIP(paramContext);
+      if (paramContext == null) {
+        throw new Exception("get server ip error");
+      }
+    }
+    catch (Exception paramContext)
+    {
+      paramContext.printStackTrace();
+      Log.i("MimiSDK", "cannot get server ip address");
+      return null;
+    }
+    paramContext = "http://" + paramContext + "/mimiads/core/index.php";
+    return paramContext;
+  }

+package com.mmsdk.internal;
+
+import android.util.Log;
+import java.io.IOException;
+import java.io.OutputStream;
+import java.io.PrintStream;
+import java.net.HttpURLConnection;
+import java.net.URL;
+import java.util.ArrayList;
+import java.util.Iterator;
+import java.util.List;
+import java.util.Map;

+import org.apache.http.HttpResponse;
+import org.apache.http.StatusLine;
+import org.apache.http.client.ClientProtocolException;
+import org.apache.http.client.HttpClient;
+import org.apache.http.client.entity.UrlEncodedFormEntity;
+import org.apache.http.client.methods.HttpGet;
+import org.apache.http.client.methods.HttpPost;
+import org.apache.http.impl.client.DefaultHttpClient;
+import org.apache.http.message.BasicNameValuePair;
+import org.apache.http.util.EntityUtils;
+
+public class SubmitDataByHttpClientAndOrdinaryWay
+{
+  public static final String AD_LOCATION = "lo";
+  public static final String AD_METHOD = "method";
+  public static final String AD_SIZE = "sz";
+  public static final String AD_TYPE = "tp";
+  public static final String DELETEJSONSTRING = "DETELEJSONSTRING";
+  public static final String DEVICEID = "deviceID";
+  public static final String INCREASEJSONSTRING = "INCREASEJSONSTRING";
+  public static final String JSONSTRING = "JSONSTRING";
+  public static final String LATITUDE = "Latitude";
+  public static final String LONGITUDE = "Longitude";
+  public static final String METHOD = "method";
+  public static final String PACKAGE_NAME = "pn";
+  public static final String PUBLISHER_ID = "pi";
+  private static final boolean SHOW_LOG = true;
+  private static final String TAG = "SubmitDataByHttpClientAndOrdinaryWay";
+  
+  public SubmitDataByHttpClientAndOrdinaryWay() {}
+  
+  public static String submintDataByHttpClientDoGet(Map<String, String> paramMap, String paramString)
+    throws ClientProtocolException, IOException
+  {
+    DefaultHttpClient localDefaultHttpClient = new DefaultHttpClient();
+    paramString = new StringBuilder(paramString);
+    paramString.append("?");
+    paramMap = paramMap.entrySet().iterator();
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      if (!paramMap.hasNext())
+      {
+        paramString.deleteCharAt(paramString.length() - 1);
+        paramMap = paramString.toString();
+        System.out.println(paramMap);
+        paramMap = localDefaultHttpClient.execute(new HttpGet(paramMap));
+        if (paramMap.getStatusLine().getStatusCode() != 200) {
+          break;
+        }
+        return EntityUtils.toString(paramMap.getEntity(), "UTF-8");
+      }
+      Map.Entry localEntry = (Map.Entry)paramMap.next();
+      paramString.append((String)localEntry.getKey()).append("=").append((String)localEntry.getValue());
+      paramString.append("&");
+    }
+    return null;
+  }
+  
+  public static String submintDataByHttpClientDoPost(Map<String, String> paramMap, String paramString)
+    throws ClientProtocolException, IOException
+  {
+    DefaultHttpClient localDefaultHttpClient = new DefaultHttpClient();
+    paramString = new HttpPost(paramString);
+    ArrayList localArrayList = new ArrayList();
+    if (paramMap != null) {
+      paramMap = paramMap.entrySet().iterator();
+    }
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      if (!paramMap.hasNext())
+      {
+        Log.i("SubmitDataByHttpClientAndOrdinaryWay", "parameters = " + localArrayList.toString());
+        paramString.setEntity(new UrlEncodedFormEntity(localArrayList, "UTF-8"));
+        paramMap = localDefaultHttpClient.execute(paramString);
+        if (paramMap.getStatusLine().getStatusCode() != 200) {
+          break;
+        }
+        return EntityUtils.toString(paramMap.getEntity(), "UTF-8");
+      }
+      Map.Entry localEntry = (Map.Entry)paramMap.next();
+      localArrayList.add(new BasicNameValuePair((String)localEntry.getKey(), (String)localEntry.getValue()));
+    }
+    return null;
+  }
+  
+  public static Boolean submitDataByDoGet(Map<String, String> paramMap, String paramString)
+    throws Exception
+  {
+    paramString = new StringBuilder(paramString);
+    paramString.append("?");
+    paramMap = paramMap.entrySet().iterator();
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      if (!paramMap.hasNext())
+      {
+        paramString.deleteCharAt(paramString.length() - 1);
+        paramMap = paramString.toString();
+        System.out.println(paramMap);
+        paramMap = (HttpURLConnection)new URL(paramMap).openConnection();
+        paramMap.setRequestMethod("GET");
+        paramMap.setReadTimeout(5000);
+        if (paramMap.getResponseCode() != 200) {
+          break;
+        }
+        return Boolean.valueOf(true);
+      }
+      Map.Entry localEntry = (Map.Entry)paramMap.next();
+      paramString.append((String)localEntry.getKey()).append("=").append((String)localEntry.getValue());
+      paramString.append("&");
+    }
+    return Boolean.valueOf(false);
+  }
+  
+  public static Boolean submitDataByDoPost(Map<String, String> paramMap, String paramString)
+    throws Exception
+  {
+    paramString = new URL(paramString);
+    StringBuilder localStringBuilder = new StringBuilder();
+    paramMap = paramMap.entrySet().iterator();
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      if (!paramMap.hasNext())
+      {
+        localStringBuilder.deleteCharAt(localStringBuilder.length() - 1);
+        paramMap = localStringBuilder.toString();
+        paramString = (HttpURLConnection)paramString.openConnection();
+        paramString.setRequestMethod("POST");
+        paramString.setReadTimeout(5000);
+        paramString.setDoOutput(true);
+        paramString.setRequestProperty("Content-Type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
+        paramString.setRequestProperty("Content-Length", String.valueOf(paramMap.getBytes().length));
+        paramString.getOutputStream().write(paramMap.getBytes());
+        if (paramString.getResponseCode() != 200) {
+          break;
+        }
+        return Boolean.valueOf(true);
+      }
+      Map.Entry localEntry = (Map.Entry)paramMap.next();
+      localStringBuilder.append((String)localEntry.getKey()).append("=").append((String)localEntry.getValue());
+      localStringBuilder.append("&");
+    }
+    return Boolean.valueOf(false);
+  }

+public class TimerBannerAdController
+  implements Ad
+{
+  private static final int ADHIDE = 0;
+  private static final int ADLOAD = 2;
+  private static final int ADSHOW = 1;

+  private static final int LOCATION_BOTTOM_RIGHT = 5;

+  private Handler mHandler = new Handler()
+  {
+    public void handleMessage(Message paramAnonymousMessage)
+    {
+      switch (paramAnonymousMessage.what)
+      {
+      }
+      do
+      {
+        return;
+        MyLog.i(TimerBannerAdController.TAG, "hide banner ad");
+        if (TimerBannerAdController.this.mAdObject.testMode != 1)
+        {
+          TimerBannerAdController.this.mAdLayout.setVisibility(8);
+          TimerBannerAdController.this.mAdLayout.startAnimation(TimerBannerAdController.this.hideAnimation);
+        }
+        paramAnonymousMessage = obtainMessage();
+        paramAnonymousMessage.what = 2;
+        sendMessageDelayed(paramAnonymousMessage, TimerBannerAdController.this.hideTime);
+        return;

+        }
+        for (;;)

+          paramAnonymousMessage = obtainMessage();
+          paramAnonymousMessage.what = 0;

+        }

+        TimerBannerAdController.this.mAdWebView.loadUrl(TimerBannerAdController.this.mAdUrl);

+      }
+    }

+  public TimerBannerAdController(Context paramContext, int paramInt, AdSize paramAdSize)
+  {

+          TimerBannerAdController.this.mAdListener.onFailedToReceiveAd(TimerBannerAdController.this, 0);
+        }

+    });

+  private String getAdHtmlData(AdObject paramAdObject)
+  {
+    HashMap localHashMap = new HashMap();
+    localHashMap.put("zd", String.valueOf(paramAdObject.zoneId));
+    try
+    {

+  }

+  private String getAdUrl(AdObject paramAdObject)

+  
+  private void showAdView(AdObject paramAdObject)
+  {
+    this.mAdObject = paramAdObject;
+    if ((this.mAdObject == null) || (this.mAdObject.isShow == 0)) {
+      return;
+    }
+    this.visible = true;
+    int i = AdUtils.getScreenWidth(this.mContext);
+    RelativeLayout.LayoutParams localLayoutParams = new RelativeLayout.LayoutParams(i, i * 10 / 64);
+    this.showTime = (paramAdObject.showTime * 1000);
+    this.hideTime = (paramAdObject.hideTime * 1000);
+    switch (paramAdObject.location)
+    {
+    }

+          }
+        }
+      });

+      this.mAdUrl = getAdUrl(this.mAdObject);

+        this.mAdWebView.loadUrl(this.mAdUrl);

+        this.mRootView.setVisibility(0);
+        return;

+        localLayoutParams.addRule(14);
+        this.showAnimation = AnimationUtils.getInFromTop();
+        this.hideAnimation = AnimationUtils.getOutToTop();
+        continue;
+        localLayoutParams.addRule(10);
+        localLayoutParams.addRule(9);
+        this.showAnimation = AnimationUtils.getInFromTop();

+        continue;

+        localLayoutParams.addRule(11);

+        this.hideAnimation = AnimationUtils.getOutToTop();

+        this.hideAnimation = AnimationUtils.getOutToBottom();

+        this.hideAnimation = AnimationUtils.getOutToBottom();
+      }
+      catch (Exception paramAdObject)
+      {
+        for (;;)
+        {
+          MyLog.i("load ad error");
+        }
+      }
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public boolean isReady()
+  {
+    if (this.mAdHelper != null) {
+      return this.mAdHelper.checkEnvironmentAndSettings();
+    }
+    return false;
+  }
+  
+  public void loadAd()
+  {
+    if (isReady()) {
+      this.mAdHelper.loadAdInfo(1);
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void release()
+  {
+    this.isCallRelease = true;
+    this.visible = false;
+    this.mAdHelper.cancelLoadAdInfo();
+    if (this.mAdWebView != null) {
+      this.mAdWebView.hideWebView();
+    }
+    if (this.mAdLayout != null)
+    {
+      this.mAdLayout.removeAllViews();
+      this.mAdLayout.setVisibility(8);
+    }
+    if (this.mRootView != null)
+    {
+      this.mRootView.removeAllViews();
+      this.mRootView.setVisibility(8);
+    }
+    if (this.mHandler != null) {
+      this.mHandler.removeCallbacksAndMessages(null);
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void setAdListener(AdListener paramAdListener)
+  {
+    this.mAdListener = paramAdListener;
+  }
+  
+  public void stopLoading()
+  {
+    release();
+  }

+  public static boolean checkAndroidManifest(Context paramContext)
+  {
+    PackageManager localPackageManager = paramContext.getPackageManager();
+    paramContext = paramContext.getPackageName();
+    if (localPackageManager.checkPermission("android.permission.INTERNET", paramContext) == -1)
+    {
+      MyLog.e("INTERNET permissions must be enabled in AndroidManifest.xml");
+      return false;
+    }
+    if (localPackageManager.checkPermission("android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE", paramContext) == -1)
+    {
+      MyLog.e("ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE permissions must be enabled in AndroidManifest.xml.");
+      return false;
+    }
+    return true;
+  }
+  
+  public static boolean checkNetwork(Context paramContext)
+  {
+    paramContext = (ConnectivityManager)paramContext.getSystemService("connectivity");
+    if (paramContext != null)
+    {
+      paramContext = paramContext.getActiveNetworkInfo();
+      if ((paramContext != null) && (paramContext.isConnected()) && (paramContext.getState() == NetworkInfo.State.CONNECTED)) {
+        return true;
+      }
+    }
+    MyLog.w("Current network is unavailable.");
+    return false;
+  }

+  {
+    paramContext = (ConnectivityManager)paramContext.getSystemService("connectivity");

+  }

+public class AnimationUtils
+{

+

+  {
+    TranslateAnimation localTranslateAnimation = new TranslateAnimation(1, 1.0F, 1, 0.0F, 1, 0.0F, 1, 0.0F);
+    localTranslateAnimation.setDuration(500L);
+    return localTranslateAnimation;
+  }
+  
+  public static Animation getInFromBottom()
+  {
+    TranslateAnimation localTranslateAnimation = new TranslateAnimation(1, 0.0F, 1, 0.0F, 1, 1.0F, 1, 0.0F);
+    localTranslateAnimation.setDuration(1000L);
+    return localTranslateAnimation;
+  }
+

+  {
+    TranslateAnimation localTranslateAnimation = new TranslateAnimation(1, -1.0F, 1, 0.0F, 1, 0.0F, 1, 0.0F);
+    localTranslateAnimation.setDuration(500L);
+    return localTranslateAnimation;
+  }
+

+package com.mmsdk.utils;
+
+import android.content.Context;
+import android.net.ConnectivityManager;
+import android.net.NetworkInfo;
+import android.net.NetworkInfo.State;
+import java.io.IOException;
+import org.apache.http.HttpResponse;
+import org.apache.http.StatusLine;
+import org.apache.http.client.HttpClient;
+import org.apache.http.client.methods.HttpHead;
+import org.apache.http.impl.client.DefaultHttpClient;
+
+public class ConnectionUtils
+{
+  public ConnectionUtils() {}
+  
+  public static boolean checkNet(Context paramContext)
+  {
+    paramContext = (ConnectivityManager)paramContext.getSystemService("connectivity");
+    if (paramContext != null)
+    {
+      paramContext = paramContext.getActiveNetworkInfo();
+      if ((paramContext != null) && (paramContext.isConnected()) && (paramContext.getState() == NetworkInfo.State.CONNECTED)) {
+        return true;
+      }
+    }
+    return false;
+  }
+  
+  public static boolean checkWifiIsOn(Context paramContext)
+  {
+    paramContext = (ConnectivityManager)paramContext.getSystemService("connectivity");
+    return (paramContext != null) && (paramContext.getNetworkInfo(1).getState() == NetworkInfo.State.CONNECTED);
+  }
+  
+  public static int getRespStatus(String paramString)
+    throws IOException
+  {
+    paramString = new HttpHead(paramString);
+    return new DefaultHttpClient().execute(paramString).getStatusLine().getStatusCode();
+  }
+}

+package com.mmsdk.utils;
+
+import java.io.PrintStream;
+import java.security.MessageDigest;
+
+public class MD5Utils
+{
+  public MD5Utils() {}
+  
+  public static String convertMD5(String paramString)
+  {
+    paramString = paramString.toCharArray();
+    int i = 0;
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      if (i >= paramString.length) {
+        return new String(paramString);
+      }
+      paramString[i] = ((char)(paramString[i] ^ 0x74));
+      i += 1;
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public static void main(String[] paramArrayOfString)
+  {
+    paramArrayOfString = new String("");
+    System.out.println("原始：" + paramArrayOfString);
+    System.out.println("MD5后：" + string2MD5(paramArrayOfString));
+    System.out.println("加密的：" + convertMD5(paramArrayOfString));
+    System.out.println("解密的：" + convertMD5(convertMD5(paramArrayOfString)));
+  }
+  
+  public static String string2MD5(String paramString)
+  {
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      Object localObject;
+      byte[] arrayOfByte;
+      int i;
+      try
+      {
+        localObject = MessageDigest.getInstance("MD5");
+        paramString = paramString.toCharArray();

+        i = 0;
+        if (i >= paramString.length)
+        {
+          paramString = ((MessageDigest)localObject).digest(arrayOfByte);
+          localObject = new StringBuffer();
+          i = 0;
+          if (i < paramString.length) {
+            break label86;
+          }
+          return ((StringBuffer)localObject).toString();
+        }
+      }
+      catch (Exception paramString)
+      {
+        System.out.println(paramString.toString());
+        paramString.printStackTrace();
+        return "";
+      }
+      arrayOfByte[i] = ((byte)paramString[i]);
+      i += 1;
+      continue;
+      label86:
+      int j = paramString[i] & 0xFF;
+      if (j < 16) {

+      }
+      ((StringBuffer)localObject).append(Integer.toHexString(j));
+      i += 1;
+    }
+  }
